snippet.title: Unknown 9: Awakening – Live Action Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch Haroona, portrayed by Anya Chalotra, awaken her Umbric potential in Unknown 9: Awakening's new Live-Action Trailer.

Your journey begins October 18, when the game launches on PlayStation, Xbox and PC via Steam. Pre-order now: https://bnent.eu/Preorder-Unknown9A
